us/" rel="tag">Marco Angius</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/tomas-mowes/" rel="tag">Tomas Mwes</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/wolfgang-rihm/" rel="tag">Wolfgang Rihm</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Anna Maria Sarra, Daniel Kirch, Henning Brockhaus, Jakob Lenz, Marco Angius, Opera lirica, Tomas Mwes, Wolfgang Rihm"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/6699ffadacad646736fb668601ae4e49" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/soundcloud-150x150.jpg" width="100" height="100" alt="redazioneGBopera" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="redazione GBopera"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/redazionegbopera/">View all articles by redazioneGBopera</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/04/the-life-and-death-of-marina-abramovic/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> &#8220;The Life and Death of Marina Abramovic&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/04/la-didone-opening-night-at-the-theatre-des-champs-elysees-in-paris/" rel="next">&#8220;La Didone&#8221;, opening night at the Thtre des Champs Elyses in Paris <span clas